mermaid

Copy code

flowchart TD

    Start([User Starts])

    Login{Login?}

    AuthMCP[MCP Auth]

    AuthOK{Auth Success?}

    NewJob{New Job Description?}

    ParseJD[Parse Job Desc]

    QNA[Q&A with User (Text/Voice)]

    ResumeGen[Generate Resume]

    UserReview{User Happy?}

    EditQnA[Edit/Redo Q&A]

    Save[Save to Cloud]

    Share[Download/Share/Apply]

    End([End])



    Start --> Login

    Login --> AuthMCP

    AuthMCP --> AuthOK

    AuthOK -- No --> Start

    AuthOK -- Yes --> NewJob

    NewJob -- Yes --> ParseJD

    ParseJD --> QNA

    QNA --> ResumeGen

    ResumeGen --> UserReview

    UserReview -- No --> EditQnA

    EditQnA --> QNA

    UserReview -- Yes --> Save

    Save --> Share

    Share --> End

    NewJob -- No --> QNA

